nodes.description: Create an exhaustive HTML travel handbook with maps, attraction descriptions, essential Japanese phrases, travel tips, and the itinerary.
nodes.agent_prompt: Create a comprehensive and exhaustive HTML travel handbook. The handbook should include the 7-day Japan itinerary from `detailed_itinerary_T006`, maps of Tokyo, Kyoto, and Nara from `maps_tokyo_kyoto_nara_T008`, descriptions of attractions from `attraction_descriptions_T009`, and essential Japanese phrases and travel tips from `japanese_phrases_travel_tips_T007`. Design the handbook with a professional, user-friendly layout that is easily navigable and accessible on mobile devices. Ensure all information is presented clearly and accurately. Include interactive maps and a table of contents for easy navigation. The final output must be an HTML file, named Japan_Travel_Guide.html with fully functional and responsive design. Create exhaustive HTML document to fulfill the request.
